# Cursor Rules — sqlserver_copilot

## Project
NASDAQ ML training pipeline. Gradient Boosting classifier → Buy/Sell predictions for NASDAQ 100 stocks.

## Stack
- Python 3.11+, scikit-learn, pandas, numpy, pyodbc
- SQL Server (localhost\MSSQLSERVER01, stockdata_db, Windows Auth)

## Architecture
- feature_engineering.py → 50+ features from OHLCV data
- feature_selection.py → SelectKBest top-20
- train_model.py → Gradient Boosting Classifier training
- predict_daily.py → Daily predictions → ml_trading_predictions table
- VARCHAR price columns — ALWAYS CAST to FLOAT

## Output Tables
- ml_trading_predictions (ticker, date, signal, confidence, strength, RSI, probabilities)
- ml_prediction_summary (daily aggregates)
- ml_technical_indicators (indicator snapshots)

## Schedule
- 6:00 AM daily predictions
- 6:30 AM freshness check + conditional retrain
- Weekly full retrain

## Ecosystem
Part of 7-repo trading platform:
- stockanalysis — data ingestion
- sqlserver_copilot_nse — NSE ML
- sqlserver_copilot_forex — Forex ML
- sqlserver_mcp — MCP bridge
- stockdata_agenticai — CrewAI agents (consumer)
- streamlit-trading-dashboard — visualization (consumer)
